    "title": "Looking for Real Estate Agent at Rustomjee Group",
    "description": "Rustomjee Group has an exciting opening for a Real Estate Agent at our Dhanbad office. Join a company that values innovation, collaboration, and continuous learning.\n\nAbout Rustomjee Group:\nRustomjee Group is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Provide advisory services on property investment and market trends\n• Liaise with banks and NBFCs for home loan assistance to customers\n• Manage RERA documentation and compliance requirements\n• Achieve monthly and quarterly sales targets\n• Source and close property deals with prospective buyers and investors\n• Build relationships with channel partners and brokers\n• Conduct land acquisition due diligence and feasibility studies\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• CA / CMA / CFA certification\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in AutoCAD\n• Proficiency in Property Management\n• Proficiency in Financial Modeling\n• Proficiency in Lease Administration\n• Proficiency in Contract Management\n• Proficiency in Market Research\n• Proficiency in Property Valuation\n• Proficiency in Real Estate Law\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Dhanbad, Jharkhand, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Rustomjee Group!",
